name: Bridget Jane
description: I am new to this and not sure how to present myself. I come from a rough past but I don’t want to live in the past but today ..the present. It’s what we can make of our presence that you will know me and I will know you. That’s said…you will not be disappointed. I’d like to have fun but can’t unless you do too. It will be you who will make our fun times special because just having met you will be special enough for me.
